data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in the heart of a tranquil and inviting neighborhood. This extraordinary home boasts 5 spacious bedrooms and 4.5 bathrooms, providing generous living space for you and your family. Located just south of Barry road, you will find this home and community located close to everything you and your family will need. Minutes from the airport, highways, shopping, restaurants, and many family entertainment options.

You'll love the open and inviting layout, featuring two elegant living spaces. The main floor living room offers a comfortable space for relaxation and social gatherings, while the second-floor loft provides a breathtaking view of the main entryway, adding a touch of grandeur to your home.

New paint and contemporary light fixtures create a warm and elegant atmosphere throughout the home, setting the stage for memorable moments with family and friends.

If cooking and entertaining are things you love, then the open-concept kitchen is sure to impress. With an island for casual dining and an adjacent eat-in area, this kitchen is the perfect hub for hosting gatherings and meal prep with your family.

Step out onto the charming rear deck, where you can savor your morning coffee or host unforgettable family BBQ’s. The walk-out basement enhances the entertainment potential providing a quiet place to sit and relax, featuring a family room with a wet bar - an entertainer's dream space. Additionally, there's an extra room that can be tailored to your specific needs, whether it's an office, gym, or craft room.

Convenience is key with main-floor laundry and a spacious three-car garage that includes a plug for your EV, ensuring that daily living is effortless and well-organized.

This home blends the best of luxury living, with the serenity of a quiet neighborhood. 

Don't miss the opportunity to make it your own. Schedule a showing today and experience the epitome of modern elegance, comfort, and spacious living.
